                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Arab and Israeli Military Commanders in the Jerusalem area signed an
                    agreement on July 7, 1948, for the demilitarization of Mount Scopus. Two
                    officials of the United Nations were also signatories; for the text of the
                    agreement, see <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss>, <hi rend="italic">8th yr.,
                        Suppl. for April, May and June 1953</hi>, page 30.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
